text: Amber English (born October 25, 1989) is an American sport shooter. She participated at the 2018 ISSF World Shooting Championships, winning a medal.Skeet results Amber has qualified for the 2020 Olympic Games to be held in Tokyo, Japan. Due to the 2020 COVID-19 (Coronavirus) pandemic, all sports for the Olympics will compete in 2021. ==References== ==External links== * Category:Living people Category:1989 births Category:American female sport shooters Category:Skeet shooters Category:Sportspeople from Colorado Springs, Colorado
